        "Description": "An interesting one, 47.\r\rOur client for this contract is Don Yates. He has recently learned that several members of his security team are leaking private information to rival law firms. Normally, he would take them to court and &quot;sue their asses,&quot; his words, not mine, or have his own sniper team take care of it, but doesn&apos;t want this getting out. As such, he has hired us to &quot;patch up the leak.&quot; Again, his words, not mine. He&apos;s hosting a party soon, which will be a good opening for us.\r\rGood luck.",
